{{wikipediapar|Firewall (construction)}}
{{en-noun}}

# A [[fireproof]] [[barrier]] used to [[prevent]] the [[spread]] of [[fire]] through a [[building]], aircraft or vehicle.
# {{computing}} The [[software]] that [[monitor]]s [[traffic]] in and out of a [[private]] [[network]] or a [[personal computer]] and [[allow]]s or [[block]]s such traffic depending on its [[perceive]]d [[threat]].

